<h2 style="color:white; font-family:verdana; font-size:50px; text-align:center;">Welcome to AgedBook 📕✍📖 </h2>
<hr />
<br />
<p class="yazi">

    This webpage enables sharing and exchanging the previously read or redundant books for free. It is a book donation platform that offers access to the books a person is looking for and it also has  different categories. Our website brings great advantage for people who are in a bad financial situation and still need to access various books. In this way, people can easily reach out the  books that they need and take advantage of them without any charges. Our hopes are high that it will be a platform that will help to increase the knowledge sharing between people. Every person can reach the books on ads that near to them as location. People from all ages can use this platform. It is very important especially for the student communities. In our country, this site has gained a huge significance for those who need the books which are being used for the exams in universities or in high schools, and those books can be attained from the book ads every moment. It was designed for transferring information and fostering solidarity between people. This site aims to keep reading real books alive instead of the digital ones.
</p>

